ComicInfo.Summary: With the Almighty Decimator outside a Capital Building held hostage by Nickelhead's Super-Villain Congress, only by conceding fully to his wacky demands will our collective hunger be satisfied. Meanwhile, in the farthest reaches of space, Adam Archer has found his sister! But at what price? Even the strange and wonderful creature known only as Lucky hears the clock ticking down! All this, and the butterfly, too!
